00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:29.500
[Robert Winston]
It is the most mysterious part of the human body

00:03:29.600 --> 00:03:33.000
And yet it dominates the way we live our adult lives

00:03:33.100 --> 00:03:35.000
It is the brain.

